::Striker::

Striker keeps his lips on Spears, wondering if she wanted to go any farther. 
One of his arms travels down her body, feeling her as the other pressed her 
to him. The fact that they were both covered with soot and ashes made holding 
her a bit accuard, but he didn't care.

His spark was speeding, his pulse going more and more rapidly, but he could 
feel that she was excited as well. He presses her body to his, continuing the 
kiss.
